# Ladder Skip

This skip is used in **every category** that goes through the [Archives](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/the-duke-s-archives). It **allows** the player **to save** a few seconds compared to using the ladder and provides a potentially easier **RTSR setup** for [Seath](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/seath-the-scaleless).

## Resources

Glitchless ladder skip options : [https://youtu.be/x_Ga7EAneOE](https://youtu.be/x_Ga7EAneOE) by m3dic on YouTube.

Glitched ladder skip options : [https://youtu.be/O0KVAclt9k8](https://youtu.be/O0KVAclt9k8) by San on YouTube.

